{
  "texts": [
    "Indeed LLMs appear to be able to reason about abstract sequences of integers or even ASCII codes.",
    "LLMs for Optimization.",
    "Related to our work, Nie et al. [33], Yang et al.",
    "[45], Zhang et al. [46] show that LLMs can be turned into textbased optimizers.",
    "Our work extends this line of work and shows that they can also be transformed into a recombination operator for ES and are capable of optimizing small neural networks."
  ]
}